    [ ] Also make the Bytes-less version inaccessible.
  [ ] tree-sitter-duat-text is not being used.
  [ ] For now, on Windows, duat can only reload if there is only one instance open.
  [ ] Overlays can't remove previous Forms early.
  [ ] Sometimes the Completions randomly don't open right away on prompt line.
  [ ] Diagnostics randomly triggers an integer overflow probably.

